    public class Player
extends nl.han.ica.oopg.objects.AnimatedSpriteObject
implements nl.han.ica.oopg.collision.ICollidableWithTiles, nl.han.ica.oopg.collision.ICollidableWithGameObjects
    This is the class for the player. It keeps track of held keys and moves the player. It is collidible with tiles to stop it from entering walls. It is the only object that handles object collission, which it uses to pick up boosters and get damaged by enemies. It keeps track of player hitpoints and score. It is created at game start by ObjectSpawner
